description: The GraphCode represents the scene where Maria and her daughter are sailing on a lake. 'Maria' is the subject (type 1), 'daughter' is the daughter (type 3), 'sail' is the activity (type 4) performed by 'Maria', and 'lake' is the location (type 2) where the activity takes place. The relationship 'perform' (type 8) links 'Maria' to 'sail', and 'target' (type 9) connects 'sail' to 'lake'.
